726080f-a.title: Queens: Astoria Boulevard - Sound Street
726080f-a.text:
Astoria Boulevard, north side, at the head of 44th Street, showing old frame dwellings as seen from the south side of the thoroughfare. The cleared area between the two houses warka the course of an old street. It is designated as Sound Street in the
1937 noning aaps of New York City.
P. L. Sperr  March 14, 1931
